   <h4 class="rtit">Welcome</h4>
   <p class="Etxt">
Hello and welcome to my homepage!<br>
<!--I am currently a Full Professor in
    the <a href=http://www.ece.uic.edu/ target=_blank>Department of Electrical and Computer
    Engineering</a>, with adjunct appointment in the
    <a href=http://www.cs.uic.edu/ target=_blank>Department
    of Computer Science</a>, at the
    <a href=http://www.uic.edu/ target=_blank>University of Illinois at Chicago</a>.-->
    I joined UIC in 1999, after
    four years with <a href=http://www.stevens-tech.edu/ target=_blank>Stevens
        Institute of Technology</a> (1995-1999) and two years
    with <a href=http://www.gm.com/vision/design_technology/research_developmentlab.html target=_blank>General Motors
        Research & Development Center</a> (1993-1995).
    UIC is only a few blocks away  from the beautiful
<a href=http://www.windycityart.com/chicago/around_chicago.htm target=_blank>downtown of Chicago</a>.


